- Build and train a UDE that recovers Glen's creep parameter $A(T)$ from velocity data — live, in
  about half a minute.
- Connect the toy to the real thing: Bolibar et al. (2023) and [ODINN.jl](https://github.com/ODINN-SciML/ODINN.jl).

